  • Method Details

    • fetchFlightsFromToAt

      public static List<Flight> fetchFlightsFromToAt(String from, String to, String date)
      A wrapper method used to retrieve flights from one location to another at a specific date.
      Parameters:
      from - The name of the departure location formatted in "name (IATA)"
      to - The name of the arrival location formatted in "name (IATA)"
      date - The date at which the flights are to be retrieved
      Returns:
      A list of 5 or more flights from "from" to "to" at "date", which (if the API does not find any real flights) are stocked up by dummy flights

    • getSuggestions

      public static String[] getSuggestions(String city)
      A method used for autocompletion of city names in the client
      Parameters:
      city - The name of a city (typed in by the user)
      Returns:
      A string array of city suggestions (retrieved by the Airlabs API)
